{
  "stem": "27507.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were doing things like, like doing clothes, and probably a family would be doing bits of clothes or some particular part of it in their own little flat.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They would be having a workshop there and working very hard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there was already-- so that part of Warsaw was already before the war tightly populated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were probably-- I don't know how many, but there must have been there maybe quarter of a million in-- in that area, something like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But now it was possibly almost doubled.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was probably in the winter of 1940, '41, they might have been up to-- there were more than 400,000.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were maybe closer to half a million.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was because all those people were brought from other parts of Warsaw to start and from the outside Warsaw, from the towns and villages around Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So it really was-- ghetto was--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a really crowded place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You went in a street, and the street was crowded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were everywhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't pass in the pavement, particularly in the main streets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You-- the pavements were full.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The roads were full.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no transport in the-- there were no cars unless there were some German car belonged to the Germans passing by.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But otherwise, I don't think there were any cars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a tram, but even the electric trams were-- which were passing through the ghetto, were not stopping and not to be used by the Jews.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there were trams which-- then in the ghetto itself, there was transport which was arranged all by big and small way by the Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were carts.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were some horse carts, I think, but not so many, I think.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it was-- no, it didn't stop.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
